These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | skateboard | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, accountant
1. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Job   | fisherman | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, house
1. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Music-Genre   | house | r&b |

 #################################

 
